These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Sport: parkour, handball
House: art-deco, modern
1. House:art-deco is in an even position##4
2. House:modern == Sport:handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Sport   | handball | parkour |
| House     | modern    | art-deco   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Nationality: indian, australian
Music-Genre: metal, jazz
1. Music-Genre:metal is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:australian is on the left of Nationality:indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Nationality   | australian | indian        |
| Music-Genre      | metal  | jazz |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: photography, gardening
Pet: turtle, rabbit
1. Pet:turtle is in an odd position##4
2. Hobby:gardening is on the left of Hobby:photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Hobby   | gardening    | photography |
| Pet   | turtle | rabbit |

